 The MME arm will build upon the traditional usual curriculum at the medical school.

 The MME is a multi-modal educational intervention of a series of interactive learning components focused on integrated weight management counseling.

 This MME intervention for weight management counseling uses the 5As model based on the updated American Heart Association (AHA) /American College of Cardiology (ACC) /The Obesity Society (TOS) and updated NHLBI guidelines.

